column5: Great time with great company.        It was hard waking up to this every morning      The only fish of the weekend              Off to another mini OFC G2G on Friday
I never woke up to that view Dan, you're cabin was in the way....Hahahahahahaha.
Good pics Dan, thanks, and it was good to meet you  Maureen
Thanks for sharing those pics!  Certainly missed seeing everyone this year!  Seems lack of fish was the common thread...but that weekend isn't just about the fish!
looks like a great weekend there
Great putting a face to a name Dan.  Hope ya had a great time and cane make it again next year.
